<p>The 51-year-old pop diva - who boasts 243.7M social media followers - captioned her snap: 'Feeling golden. Holding on to the last few moments of summer.'</p>

<p>When she's in New York, Jennifer relies on fitness trainer David Kirsch to help her maintain her impressively fit 5ft6in figure.  </p>

