<p>'I am 100% convinced that working out is part of what makes me so happy,' Lopez gushed to Hello! in 2016.</p>

<p>'Dance has always been a huge part of my life and taking the time to move my body and do something that's so good for me is key to my happiness.</p>

<p>'And I really believe that when you take care of yourself and work to stay healthy, you're better able to take care of those you love. So working out is definitely a priority for me.'</p>

<p>The former Fly Girl drinks lots of water and has a clean organic high-protein, nutrient-dense diet containing no caffeine or processed/refined foods.    </p>

