<p>I'm a very social person and love spending time with my friends and family, so when we go out to eat I try to make healthy choices,' JLo told the mag.</p>

<p>'Most restaurants offer healthy, low-calorie meals so I watch for things on the menu that fit my lifestyle. I'll have a salad or some fish with veggies. And I make sure I drink lots of water throughout the meal.'</p>

<p>It's hard to believe the Hustlers actress is mother to 12-year-old twins Max &amp; Emme Muñiz (with ex-husband #3 Marc Anthony), whom she raises with fiancé Alex Rodriguez and his two daughters (with ex-wife Cynthia Scurtis).</p>

<p>Following their March 9, 2019 engagement, Jennifer and the 45-year-old retired New York Yankee's long-delayed church nuptials have been 'on pause' due to the coronavirus pandemic.  </p>

